## 1. Completion Status
One of:
- `Completion Status: COMPLETE`
- `Completion Status: INCOMPLETE`

If incomplete, include:
- `blocking_issue`
- `missing_artifacts`
- `completed_artifacts`

## 2. Dimension Inventory
Include all candidate dimensions and their classifications.

